    • Method Detail

      • create

        Transport create(java.net.URI uri)
          throws java.io.IOException
        Creates the transport for given URI.

        Note that the case-insensitive scheme part of the URI must be one of ws, wss, http or https

        Parameters:
        uri - The URI of the WebSocket endpoint on the server side.
        Returns:
        A transport for given URI.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - Failed to create a socket. Or, HTTP proxy handshake or SSL handshake failed.
